    "title": "FactoCord 3.1.0 - Ghost Mode & PlayerWatcher Overhaul",
    
    // Release description (Markdown supported)
    "description": `## New Features

### Ghost Mode
- **Complete Invisibility**: Players can hide completely
- **Fake Login/Logout**: Sends fake logout when activating, fake login when deactivating
- **Fake Playtime**: Displays manipulated playtime
- **Pre-Login Mode**: Ghost mode can be activated before logging in
- **Auto-Silent Commands**: Configurable commands that are automatically executed silently

### PlayerWatcher Overhaul
- **Config-based Messages**: All messages are now configurable in config.json
- **Prefix-based Commands**: Now uses the configured prefix instead of hardcoded \`!player\`
- **Admin Command**: \`player_admin\` also shows hidden Ghost Mode players
- **Playtime Display**: Automatic playtime display on leave events
- **No More Discord Channel Monitoring**: Now monitors Factorio log directly

### Technical Improvements
- Complete log suppression for Ghost Mode (including console channel)
- New config options for PlayerWatcher messages
- Removed \`player_watcher_source_channel_id\` config option
- Spy mode now works correctly in control.lua

## Config Changes

### New Config Options:
\`\`\`json
{
  "messages": {
    "player_watcher_join": "**Join:**\\n{username} hat sich eingeloggt",
    "player_watcher_leave": "**Leave:**\\n{username} hat sich ausgeloggt",
    "player_watcher_leave_time": "**Leave:**\\n{username} (Spielzeit: {playtime})",
    "player_list_header": "**Aktive Spieler:** {count}",
    "player_list_entry": "- {username}: online seit {playtime}",
    "player_list_empty": "Es sind derzeit keine Spieler online."
  }
}
\`\`\`

### Removed Config Options:
- \`player_watcher_source_channel_id\` (no longer needed)

## New Commands

- \`$ghost on\` - Activate Ghost Mode
- \`$ghost off\` - Deactivate Ghost Mode
- \`$ghost prelogin\` - Schedule Ghost Mode for next login
- \`$ghost commands\` - Manage Auto-Silent Commands
- \`$player_admin\` - Show all players including Ghost Mode players (admins only)

## Installation

1. Download \`FactoCord3.zip\` and extract it
2. Copy the new \`control.lua\` to your Factorio scenario
3. Update your \`config.json\` with the new options (see config-example.json)
4. Restart FactoCord

## Breaking Changes

- \`player_watcher_source_channel_id\` has been removed - only use \`player_watcher_target_channel_id\`
- \`!player\` command now uses the configured prefix (default: \`$player\`)
